title: Kane, Griezmann, Götze and Fabregas in B [READY] f. “Firestarter” by The Prodigy | Beats by Dre
description:
Watch Antoine Griezmann, Mario Götze, Harry Kane and Cesc Fabregas use Beats and The Prodigy’s "Firestarter" to get ready for this summer's tournament. The music focuses their minds and transports them into the "Firestarter" music video where they face off against their opponents, visualising victory in the game ahead. When they step out on to the pitch, they are #READY to win.

Featuring: The Prodigy
See the original music video for "Firestarter"
